Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
How do you do?
Hello
Hello, how can I help?
I would like to view an apartment.
You suddenly remember that you have a friend's wedding on Sunday at 6 pm. [instruction 2 of 6]
What is your name?
Could you give me your name, please?
My name is Alexis.
Ask something about the apartment, or engage in smalltalk, or make a joke. [instruction 3 of 6]
What is the apartment name?
What apartment are you interested in?
I would like to see the North Hill Apartments on Sunday.

You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee. Find a way to make an appointment anyway. If no date is available, change date and/or time until something works. If you already got the appointment, engage in smalltalk. [instruction 4 of 6]
What start time
When would you like the viewing to start?
Well before 6 pm please because I have a wedding to attend then.
Once you've scheduled the viewing, say something about your friend's wedding. [instruction 5 of 6]
Did you pay application fee?
Have you already paid the application fee for the apartment?
I think I did, but I cannot recall.
When you are done with all the instructions, bring the conversation to a natural close.  [instruction 6 of 6]
Any custom message?
Would you like to add a message for the letting agency?
I just would like to know prior if I had yet to pay the fee.
Fee is paid.
Fee is paid.
Excellent. I have so much to look forward to on Sunday now. An apartment tour and a friend's wedding. Exciting!
